\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No clubs or friends that she used to go out with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself at all - like your father did to the theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 She'd go with him. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 She was interested in that sort of thing too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes. That's all there was to get - to go to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - about - about half past five to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How many evenings in the week would you say he'd go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Perhaps only once or twice. One - each place. One theatre and one variety show.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did he ever go to a club or a pub at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. He didn't drink at all. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your father take part in any sport or did he attend the races or place any bets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No vices?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not that I know of.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, the boot, sick and funeral clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not that I know of. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you get on with your brother and sister as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh we'd have squabbles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 But reasonably well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was there one of them that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 My brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You felt closer to your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 As a child who did you play with - would you have played mainly with your brother and sister of the neighbours children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - all together. Boys and girls. Yes. Four or five of us. When we had time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When you weren't practicing your music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When we weren't - aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Where would you play - would you have played in a yard or a garden if you had one, or in the street or other homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 There was a large field just - by where we lived and we all played there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 This was a convenient spot for the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What games did you play - can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Cricket - peggy. Do you know peggy? It's a piece of a brush shank about - about six inches long, point
ed at both ends. You had to it at the point, it'd jump up. You had - you'd to knock it - so far that - so many - we all got to a certain place and the least number of hits was the winner. It was called peggy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Any others you can think of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh marbles. We used to play marbles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - I don't think we were ever clean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You can't remember being told off for getting dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh we'd get told off. But we didn't have much time to play. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 This was particularly because you were a musical family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
That's right. My brother was doing about eight hours a day on the violin and - sister was doing about eight on - eight hours on the piano. He didn't do anything 'til he was twenty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Your parents didn't discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 That's something I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you belong to any youth organi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7763575\charrsid12918160 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 ations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you have any hobbies - did you keep any pets or collect anything or do any gardening or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, we just had a dog as pet, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Who's pet was he particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh all - all of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Cricket - now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 But not a sort of regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And you went to the theatres and concerts - would you have gone to musical concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 It would be a musical concert. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What about cinemas while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well there weren't any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Just the magic lantern slides?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes, and they were - sometime getting a magic lantern. We were - we were old enough to - go ourselves to magic lantern shows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 So it was quite late on then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Perhaps - eight or nine I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What would that have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 About threepence a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you get that regularly every Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What would you have spent that on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - sweets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family - any relations - friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Just - a woman came in two or three days a week. To clean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 But apart from that can you remember anybody?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
No, no one else. Oh - a - a next door neighbour who - would take - take us out at times. But I remember her dropping me from a wall into a - about ten feet below onto a brick and she did this when I was three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did she come to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
I don't know. But it was a wall - about three feet high and underneath it was a - a stream running. I - I fell off this wall into this stream and she did this to me. I remember that to this day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 If your mother was ill or confined to bed, how d
id she manage - can you remember her being ill or confined to bed or perhaps having another child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I don't remember her being ill until - until she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember what happened when your younger brother was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Older brother. Oh - no, couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Only at Maryport.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not in Carlisle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How much would you have seen of your relatives as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - perhaps two or three times a year, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not very frequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would they come to you or would you go to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Come to us - we went to them now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When would they have seen them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - well they lived quite near - two or three nights a week maybe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would they come to them or would your parents go to their homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They only went to each others houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Come both ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did they share the same friends or did they have separate friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh no, shared friends. Mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink when they came to your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh they'd have something to eat probably - nothing to drink. No intoxicating - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did friends ever call in casually without an invitation?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes, oh these - they just pop in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What about neighbours - would neighbours have done the same?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well these are neighbours I'm speaking of. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 People tell us that in those days they made their own amusements - wh
at do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends and neighbours - would they have had musical evenings together or would they have played games or just talked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - as far as we were concerned it was musical evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would your parents have joined in this sort of thing too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, they just sat and listened. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Neither of them played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did you think of 
some people belonging to one and some to another group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Which class or group would you say you belonged to yourself in those early days, would you be able to say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No ideas? Could you think of what sort of people belonged to the same class group as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - these friends that used to call - he was in the - income tax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And you'd put him in the same class as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you think of any people belonging to certain classes or groups of 
people - can you put any section of the people that you knew then into certain classes in your mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, I couldn't tell you anything about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were you ever taught to touch your cap or show respect in some way to people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 To lift your cap. To ladies. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Only to ladies or to people older than yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 To the ladies. That's all I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was there anyone you called Sir or Master or Madam as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 We always called the doctor Sir. But I don't remember anyone else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Perhaps these friends that would call.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They would say Sir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
In the district or village where you lived who were considered the most important people? If you could leave Carlisle out of that question and think of yourself living in Liverpool when you were seventeen - in that particular par
t of Liverpool who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
To me? I really had no time for anything except playing. I was playing most nights. And - business in the daytime. My day was full for years and years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When you were in Liverpool, who would you have thought shopkeepers associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Probably other business people. I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And what about the clergy - who would their friends have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Other clergy. I'd - I would have thought so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What about teachers and farmers and employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I should think they would have kept to their own particular class - farmers with farmers and teachers and teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What sort of people would you say went to the church when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well I should say they were all sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 A real mixture?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember any friction between Catholics and Protestants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember any when you were living in Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Only - only as today. If you can call that friction.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember any particular incidents that you witnessed or heard about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No. Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Where you lived did all the people in the working class group have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups in that group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I wouldn't like to say. I didn't know too much about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you think that one group felt itself superior in any way to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you think some families were thought of as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - what I would call respectable yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How would you describe a rough family then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well not so well off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And respectable? Would they have to be better off or better behaved to be respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Bit of both maybe. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes or groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another - did people do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, I couldn't say about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No thoughts on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I can't think of anybody except the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would you have described his as a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Why would you have said that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh well I don't know, he was - he was - gentle and kind - don't know - don't recollect much about him except he was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 This was the impression you got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 That was the impression I got about him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, very - very occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What did you think of policemen generally when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I didn't think about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your mother ever threaten you with - I'll tell a policeman if you don't behave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you ever recall thinking how he treated people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well I - I think the people - the policeman treated people badly at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You don't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. Not like today. They have - they haven't the work to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was your home rented when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. It was - belonged to father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle it make ends meet at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You say you couldn't remember your father being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well you're not in a government job are you.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 If he was ever ill when you were a child can you remember what difference it made to the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 If he was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you remember him being ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Only once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did it make much difference to the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Money}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7763575\charrsid12918160 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
