\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Do you think - you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Whilst you were at school did you do any part time jobs or anything to earn a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When I reached the age of - fourteen, I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Used to go playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Where would you have played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Theatre. Penrith, Keswick. Howick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you play in a band?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Orchestra.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And you were only fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you get involved in these jobs that you got playing in an orchestra?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Well I - whilst I was at Carlisle I met my teachers wife and she remember me - from about fifty years ago - and she said, when Toby was teaching him the clarinet he was teaching Toby after two years
. So I suppose I was good. Well I used to get jobs - Penrith, with the Cumberland Orchestral Society. Keswick, Howick. Paid for it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How much would you have been paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh, perhaps a guinea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 For each time you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Used to play at dances as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How many hours would you have worked in a week at this sort of thing when you were this age? Would you have played just at weekends?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, if we played you see it would be all week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 This was before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You wouldn't go to school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes, it was only in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 In the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You wouldn't have had holidays with pay because it wouldn't have been that kind of a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No, that's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you feel the guinea that you got was a fair wage for this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - I didn't know the value of money really at that age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Going by other peoples money that was very good really wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 If it was late and I used to play dances as well. Eight 'til two a couple of evenings. That's a lot of money in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What did you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I didn't spend it - I suppose I gave it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Gave it to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - used to spend a lot of money on - the three of us. To teach us. I had five pairs of clarinets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Which your mother had bought for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Father bought them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would your mother ever give you any money back out of this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes, probably did give me a few shillings. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you get on with the other people in the orchestra when you started this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Got on quite well with them. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And you obviously liked the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - I loved it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did getting this job during school time alter your attitude to school in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Your first full time job - what did you do when you were fifteen for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I didn't have a full time job at fifteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 The only full time job I - had when I was seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What did you do then between fifteen and seventeen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Nothing. Practicing. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You mostly were at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. The three of us were practicing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were you still continuing to play an orchestra's and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 For the same sort of money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Your first full time job began at seventeen - what would that have been - you came to Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. I went as a learner - telegraphist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 With the G.P.O.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How long were you doing that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well I was there until you could do so many words a minute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How long would that have taken you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Oh - perhaps six months. Then they would offer you an appointment in another office because there was no vacancy in Carlisle. And - they offered me three places which I ref
used, then they finally offered me Liverpool. I wanted a first class office you see. That's why I came to Liverpool.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How long were you doing that at Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 'Til I retired.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 For all that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you have any different type of job with the Post Office or did you continue the same job - telegraphy - all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - it's not telegraphy now as what it was. It was all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7763575\charrsid12918160 M}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 orse in those days but - lot's of different instruments in the time I was there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 But it was the same sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes. It's all communications.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You did that up 'til you retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 '53.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 'Til you were fifty-three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 1953.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Have you done any other job since then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. Except this.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Tell me what you do here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh well this - this is a legacy. Well I lost my wife you see three years ago and I were left to carry on. We were at Woodlands from 1951.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 This was a private nursing home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. We left there in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 1958. In
}}}1958. In{\*\xmlclose} the meantime we had bought this pla
ce because we were only on a lease for eight years. We - we couldn't out from the wonder whether he would renew the lease. If he didn't we had nowhere to go so we bought this place from Doctor Timwood. We've been here ever since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 And you still run this as a running concern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 For old people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 An old people's home really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would you have preferred another type of occupation from the telegraphy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Music.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You would have preferred to have made a career of music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh - yes. Well I've been playing for - for - professionally since I was - seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You obviously served an apprenticeship or training period for the telegraphy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you belong to any trade union or professional organization?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Just the - office union of Post Office Workers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you take part in any of the activities of the union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not interested. I wasn't interested in Post Office. On - More keen on getting - playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Getting through the day and having the evening for what you wanted to do?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Many a time I didn't work more than eighteen hours in the week at the Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I was going out - I going round to places playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you get the time off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
I had to get substitution by some other member of the staff. If I were on - say nine 'til five and wanted to catch the nine thirty train I'd get somebody to do nine thirty to tree and another chap three to five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would they cover up for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Yes. I had to pay them. Yes. They - they would - they would do it so long as the chap was off at three - he wouldn't stay on 'til five for you so you owed him two hours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same i
nterests or different ones at this stage in your career when you were first with the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What sort of employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 The people who were over you in the Post Office - did you feel they had different interests from you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They didn't like me playing. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Why was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They thought I was more interested in the music than business. In - in the Post Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They were right weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They were. I had to promote - I had to promote - promote myself. You see, you had to
 be - you had to have technical certificates before you could be promoted. And - I didn't have these, I hadn't time to study but I was always interested in the subject. Chaps keep telling that - telling me I was a damn fool not to go in for them - 'cos yo
u got extra money for them. Oh, I went in for - I got them. And I got promoted about a fortnight after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers - did you feel that or not?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 A great? Are you - are you speaking about the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Generally speaking apart from the Post Office - other occupations in life, did you feel there was a tremendous difference between trained craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I would say there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You wouldn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I would. I would think there was. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How would you have felt this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - I think it still applies. An amateur is not as good as a professional - at anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No I don't think so. I liked it just as much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents or your brother and sister at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. They came to live in Liverpool.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They joined you did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 For six months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Then they went back again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Went back again. They - they didn't like the people. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They couldn't get used to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not as homely. Well - my daughter's just come back from Carlise - just yesterday. She sai
d, she was living up - she wished she was living there. Just because of the people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 They are friendly are they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you spend your Sunday any differently when you started full time work - did you still continue to go to evening service
 or did you not go at this stage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Evening service - to church - oh - slacked off a bit. We used to play clarinet quarters - Sunday after Sunday. Just for the love of it. About eight hours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you take an interest in politics at this time in your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. None at all. Not interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way or did you do different things now - you obviously continued to play and practice - but did you have any different interests at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I - yes
, I had one or two hobbies. Such as - wireless - and - some woodwork, when there was time. I made that thing there - it - that cabinet. Inside and out. Polished as well. It's just a record player now - it was a radiogram. It took me three months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you go out in the evenings apart from commitments musically wide - did you have any other interests at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 At what age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When you were a young man starting work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. No, very seldom. I hadn't many nights to go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls at this stage in your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Not new ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 When you came to Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I made friends when I moved here. Still have them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you meet these friends mainly? Were they fellow colleagues at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh most - yes, most fellows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you have any special friends at this time - did you have a girl friend for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No. Not 'til about - let me see - about 1914.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 You started to be aware of the opposite sex?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your parents meet your friends at all - when they came to Liverpool perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 No, they were only there for six months. They went back again. To Carlisle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Before you came to Liverpool, when you went out in the evenings did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Well - they always knew where we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did they expect you to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were they fairly strict about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 What age were you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5340772 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
 - you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5340772 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160  in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Twenty-five I think I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How long had you known your wife then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 About - couple of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How did you meet her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 
Well - we - I was in lodgings of course and I happened to go to a place with three colleagues - to a place where they were - in lodgings. With a 
man and his family. He was a bank manager - one of the Liverpool Savings Banks and his wife - was no more. And we - he was - they were in one room and we were in the other. That's how I got to know her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was she a Liverpool person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you save up money before getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5340772 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160  or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did your parents help you in setting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes. Both of them. Both. His parents - my wife's parents and my parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How long were you engaged to your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 About nine months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Can you describe your wedding - where were you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5340772 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 , in a church or registry office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh church - St Augustine}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7763575\charrsid12918160 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 s. Shore Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Was it a white wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did she have any bridesmaids?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 How many?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Were there many guests at the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh there was only really family. The - the parson was a relation. There was two or three. Very quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you get wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Could you remember some of the things you got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 I don't think I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you have a reception afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh it was all at home. Hampstead Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Did you have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14110983 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 Where did you go for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6047167 FA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14297171\charrsid12918160 We went to Keswick.
